#: src/migration.md:77
msgid ""
"maturin 0.13 no longer searches for Python interpreters by default and only "
"build wheels for the current Python interpreter (i.e. `python3`) in `PATH`."
msgstr ""

#: src/migration.md:80
msgid "To enable the old behavior, use the new `--find-interpreter` option."
