"Previously `--repository-url` option in `maturin upload` and `maturin "
"publish` commands accepts both repository name and URL. maturin 0.13 changed "
"`--repository-url` to only accept full URL and added a new `--repository` "
"for the repository name. This new behavior matches `twine upload`."
