msgid "CLI argument"
msgstr "CLI 引數"

#: src/sbom.md:108
msgid ""
"Additional SBOM files can also be included via the `--sbom-include` CLI "
"argument, which is useful when you only want to include SBOMs in certain "
"environments (e.g. CI) without modifying `pyproject.toml`:"
msgstr ""

#: src/sbom.md:114
